{"tid":944654,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"究竟係 同樂去踏踏步 定 陪伴著你入夢 ？","createTime":"2018-12-17T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T12:13:15.000Z","uid":73526,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c29cffb53909d9d5905de0f5ba95475dc741427f","tid":944654,"uid":73526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"猶如在夢幻國 神奇力量贈我 袋仔的百寶<br />\n<br />\n同遊萬象太空 銀河上面捕捉 光陰的美好<br />\n<br />\n難題若是遇到 隨時隨地就變身 彷彿滿腹靈感<br />\n<br />\n快飛往怡神無愁樂國<br />\n挽手跟星光閃閃跳舞<br />\n<br />\n隨意踏進這扇門 讓理想得到夢變真<br />\n越過鐵路和郊野 轉眼再現夢快車<br />\n<br />\nSha la la la la 陪伴我一起歌唱<br />\n高聲安歌 同樂去踏踏步<br />\nDoraemon 讓此刻不會老<br />\n夢境終可以達到<br />\n<br />\nSha la la la la 陪伴我一起歌唱<br />\n高聲安歌 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">陪伴著你入夢</span></span><br />\nDoraemon 讓此刻不會老<br />\n美景將可以望見得到<br />\n<br />\n我明明記得其中一段係陪伴著你入夢<br />\n但我次次咁唱都比人笑我記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮 = 有「陪伴著你入夢」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負皮 = 我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef6b794ed112d91b1533ceb899a5da2882eb978","tid":944654,"uid":87394,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:57:50.000Z","msg":"我記得係同樂去踏踏步"},{"pid":"70eae7c4d8ca79b813803d53237ecd2861ea274f","tid":944654,"uid":222727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:02:40.000Z","msg":"曼得拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b61176843e37b91c0d1ed1bad8fe29b8cd0e37a5","tid":944654,"uid":222727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曼<span style=\"color: red;\">德</span>拉效應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3877b2